OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779984666
OL,3,CWoman killed after Sheffield shooting
OL,4,Cbelieved to be 'innocent bystander'
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire police believe the 30-
OL,7,Fyear-old woman killed in a shooting in
OL,8,FSheffield was an "innocent bystander"
OL,9,Foutside of a nightclub.
OL,11,FPolice were called to reports of a
OL,12,Fshooting outside the One Four One bar
OL,13,Fin Sheffield city centre at around
OL,14,F2.45am on Monday, 25 May.
OL,16,FThe woman, from Sheffield, was found
OL,17,Fwith serious injuries. She was taken
OL,18,Fto hospital where she later died.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
