PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779984666
OL,3,CWoman killed after Sheffield shooting
OL,4,Cbelieved to be 'innocent bystander'
OL,6,FIn a statement read outside the bar on
OL,7,FTuesday, 26 May, Chief Superintendent
OL,8,FJamie Henderson said: "Following
OL,9,Fextensive enquiries over the last 36
OL,10,Fhours, we believe the victim was an
OL,11,Finnocent bystander who was on a night
OL,12,Fout in our city to celebrate the bank
OL,13,Fholiday weekend."
OL,15,FOfficers are appealing for witness and
OL,16,Finformation from anyone who was out or
OL,17,Fworking on bank holiday Sunday into
OL,18,FMonday who may have seen a white Audi
OL,19,Fin the area.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
