PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779984666
OL,3,CWoman killed after Sheffield shooting
OL,4,Cbelieved to be 'innocent bystander'
OL,6,FThree people have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder in connection with
OL,8,Fthe shooting.
OL,10,FA 30-year-old man and 32-year-old
OL,11,Fwoman were arrested near Stockport
OL,12,Fduring the early hours of this
OL,13,Fmorning, while a 30-year-old man was
OL,14,Farrested in Sheffield.
OL,16,FAll three people remain in police
OL,17,Fcustody.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
