CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779984666
OL,3,CWoman killed after Sheffield shooting
OL,4,Cbelieved to be 'innocent bystander'
OL,6,FCh Supd Henderson added: "We need your
OL,7,Fhelp. We know that West Street and
OL,8,FEldon Street were both busy at the
OL,9,Ftime of this incident, and there were
OL,10,Fpeople who saw what happened who
OL,11,Fhaven't come forward yet."
OL,13,F"We also know there are others within
OL,14,Four communities who know who is
OL,15,Fresponsible or who is involved in gun
OL,16,Fcrime but feel too scared to tell us
OL,17,Fwhat they know.
OL,19,F"(....)Gun crime causes devastation
OL,20,Fwithin families and communities.
