OL,3,CWoman killed after Sheffield shooting
OL,4,Cbelieved to be 'innocent bystander'
OL,6,F"In this case, an innocent woman who
OL,7,Fshould have been able to safely enjoy
OL,8,Fa night out in Sheffield has been
OL,9,Fkilled, and her loved ones have been
OL,10,Fleft to face the heartbreaking reality
OL,11,Fthat they will never see her again."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
